{"tid":135515,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]支那女試用電流按摩暴斃　家屬質疑儀器漏電","createTime":"2017-02-26T11:56:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T13:53:29.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8af16b04d8bfa6a2fb8d7af1f50f9bfcf5a3e12a","tid":135515,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170226/bkncn-20170226030435701-0226_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170226%2Fbkncn-20170226030435701-0226_05011_001.html&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=75188816\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170226/bkncn-20170226030435701-0226_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n湖南長沙一名36歲的彭姓女子，前日隨朋友到當地一間美容院接受電流按摩時意外死亡。彭女家屬質疑事故是儀器出現漏電，或者電流調校過高所致，惟彭女的死因至今仍未確定。目前，警方已介入調查，而涉事美容店則正與死者家屬進行協商。<br />\n<br />\n據彭女的朋友周女表示，事發當日下午，她與彭女來到雨花區的皙泉美容美體店按摩放鬆，在美容師的推薦下，試用一款名為「健康博士」的按摩儀器，但當時店內的儀器只有一台，故她便讓予彭女先體驗。惟約20分鐘後，她突然發現彭女手臂僵硬，且牙齒緊咬、嘴部發紫，遂即時為彭女急救，並呼叫救援人員，惟終無法救活彭女。<br />\n<br />\n彭女的家屬表示，彭女有一名9歲的孩子，且正打算懷二胎，故一直很注意健康，除了每年都會進行身體檢查外，平日亦有做運動的習慣，故其意外死亡，很可能是儀器漏電，或者電流調校過高所致；周女亦認同彭女家屬的質疑，並透露她在使用儀器時，曾有「身體不受控制」的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n美容院負責人回應指，美容師使用儀器時，會先將一層薄紙墊在客人皮膚上，故儀器並不會直接接觸身體。而該專案自2014年至今，仍未出現過任何問題。他又表示，「一切以屍檢報告為准，如果是我們（美容院）的責任肯定會承擔，即使不是，出於人道主義也會補償一點。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd077fa59a7bd8731fdcdb750e739941c136d9b","tid":135515,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"坐電椅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1590a72d4c19009cb58cbdbf7f5bf180a05223","tid":135515,"uid":23973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"以為俾錢電鳩條女個閪嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f7dce7e938fa704890c4105513d4dc3cc6e062","tid":135515,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43c91bc2de1114d719801d99073764a5ad66dee","tid":135515,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"睇多咗個 棒 字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4595d7a300a83f16a7cc5f352b41fb9fcd9db86","tid":135515,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇多咗個 棒 字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106d60e4fe692ef1db2ffe738d263c4ecfbf4dbb","tid":135515,"uid":47184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇多咗個 棒 字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咸濕仔x3"},{"pid":"1f3638b9830c6af08af55b558cfacb7a8561f28f","tid":135515,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}